schools.name: Dr. Henry E. Perrine Academy Of The Arts

data.description: Elegant 4 bdrm/2.5 bath home on a spacious corner lot in Palmetto Bay. Formal living & dining. Large family rm off kitchen w/ keystone, wood burning fireplace, wet bar w/hammered copper sink & built in cabinetry. Warm & inviting kitchen w/ granite counters, solid wood cabinets, pantry. Impact windows/doors. Custom baseboards & crown molding, neutral tile floors. Grand primary suite, double closets, luxurious primary bath w/ dual vanity, step-down shower w/ bench. Indoor laundry rm. Private fenced backyard w/ deep covered travertine patio, lush landscape w/ mature fruit trees: avocado, mango, guanabana, papaya & banana, fire pit, storage shed w/ electricity & AC. Room for a pool, RV/boat parking. Side entry 2 car garage, circular driveway. VA loan assumable to a qualified veteran.
